flowchart TD
  Start --> Query[Query orders where status='pending' and payment_deadline < now()]
  Query --> Check{No expired orders?}
  Check -- Yes --> End[Stop]
  Check -- No --> Process[For each expired order: Begin transaction]
  Process --> Cancel[Set order.status = 'cancelled']
  Cancel --> Decrement[Decrement ticket_type.sold by quantity]
  Decrement --> Commit[Commit transaction]
  Commit --> Log[Log actions and metrics]
  Log --> End
